public static enum Openapiv2.SecurityScheme.Flow extends Enum<Openapiv2.SecurityScheme.Flow> implements com.google.protobuf.ProtocolMessageEnum
 The flow used by the OAuth2 security scheme. Valid values are
 "implicit", "password", "application" or "accessCode".
